<p>This is pretty interesting, and a good setup to the rest of the series. Also, given that I love 354, I'm looking forward to where you take it. The problem is that for about the first half, the droid's dialogue is ridiculous. By the time I reached &quot;assuming that that's your <em>real</em> name,&quot; I'd pretty much just stopped taking this seriously, which then confused me when the rest of the tale seemed to be reasonably serious. If you do intend the whole thing to be funny, then&#8230; *shrug* I didn't feel like that came through very much. No vote for now.</p>

